Package: genefunnel
Title: Gene Set Activity Scoring with GeneFunnel
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Emir", "Turkes", email = "emir.turkes@eturkes.com",
        role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
Description: Computes sample-wise gene set activity scores from non-negative
    feature-by-sample matrices. Each score combines the sum of observed member
    values with a scaled within-set absolute-deviation penalty, independently
    for every sample and gene set. Dense and sparse matrices, partial feature
    coverage, sample-specific missing values, and parallel backends are
    supported. The package performs scoring only; it does not normalize
    measurements, map identifiers, or perform downstream statistical testing.
